article.headline: Okros scores 14, helps lead Drexel over Lafayette 69-48
article.description: — Mate Okros scored 14 points as Drexel beat Lafayette 69-48 on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Okros scores 14, helps lead Drexel over Lafayette 69-48
article.story: EASTON, Pa. -- — Mate Okros scored 14 points as Drexel beat Lafayette 69-48 on Wednesday night. Lamar Oden Jr. added 11 points and seven rebounds for the Dragons (4-3). Amari Williams finished with 10 points. The Leopards (1-7) were led in scoring by Justin Vander Baan, who finished with 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
